The paper discusses the challenges in managing complex information technology ecosystems, which suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The paper also mentions the need for algorithms and tools to transform data into relevant information, which could fall under software engineering (cs.SE) or systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses real-life examples of diagnosis, model discovery, and policy optimization, which are all topics within machine learning (cs.LG).
